            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <center>
                        <img src="https://media.formula1.com/image/upload/content/dam/fom-website/Unlocked2023/Primary_3_LiveLiteTimings_1.png" alt="F1 Logo" />
                    </center>
                </td>
                <td>
                    <div class="section-title">Unlock every detail</div>
                    <div class="section-description">Every. Detail. Covered. Immerse yourself in the race with free Live Timing data. Track your favorites with a live leaderboard and sector performance. Eavesdrop with team radio feeds.</div>
                    <button class="cta-button">Join F1 Unlocked free</button>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <div class="section-title">Unlock epic rewards</div>
                    <div class="section-description">Your name on a chequered flag. Driver wallpapers. Exclusive experiences. Access to unique rewards and giveaways is just one click away.</div>
                    <button class="cta-button">Join F1 Unlocked free</button>
                </td>
                <td>
                    <center><img src="https://media.formula1.com/image/upload/f_auto/q_auto/v1716537494/fom-website/Unlocked2024/F1_Unlocked_Website_PageHeader_V1.0_crop.jpg" alt="Tobias" /></center>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
